com.appscend.media.events

Class APSVastAdBreak

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appscend.media.APSMediaTrackableObject
      • com.appscend.media.events.APSMediaEvent
        • com.appscend.media.events.APSVastAdBreak

  • public class APSVastAdBreak
extends APSMediaEvent

    An APSVASTAdBreak object defines an ad break for which the builder plugin will try to generate APSMediaUnits and insert them into the playlist.

    Author:
    Appscend
